branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
HRZ recirculating chillers are especially suited for high technology sectors, by conforming to several SEMI equipment standards and regulating fluid temperature &#xb1;0.1&#xb0;C. All models offer compatibility with R404A and R134a refrigerants. 4 cooling capacities are available. This model requires clear or deionized water as a coolant.
&lt;/p&gt;

